  "body": "## The problem\r\n\r\nIt seems that substitions using uppercase S instead of s (return string with substitutions instead of modifying in place) is not documented.\r\n\r\n## Suggestions\r\n\r\nAdd documentation for S to the regex overview page (https://docs.perl6.org/language/regexes)\r\n\r\nEDIT: I was just told about the documentation [here](https://docs.perl6.org/language/operators#S///_non-destructive_substitution). But it probably wouldn't hurt to mention it on the regex page.",
